Location highlights:
200m to Duke St
1km to McIntyre Road
1.5km to Ballarat Road
2.5km to M80 Western Ring Road (via McIntyre Rd)
7km to Port of Melbourne
10km to CBD
10km to Melbourne Airport

+ Large yard allowing drive through truck access

+ Fitted offices, reception and amenities over two levels: 186sqm*
+ Extensive 86m* frontage to Berkshire Road
+ High clearance warehouse
+ Triple interceptor

+ Three phase power


*approx.
